          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1692807034886-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the duck is golden and the carrots are tender, remove the tray[s] from the oven</p><p>Brush some <strong>orange</strong> <strong>sauce</strong> over each duck leg and drizzle the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>honey</strong> over the carrots</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for a further 3-4 min or until glazed – this is your <strong>duck a l’orange and</strong> <strong>glazed carrots</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
