        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>duck a l’orange</strong> with the <strong>hasselback</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong> and <strong>glazed</strong> <strong>carrots</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>orange</strong> <strong>sauce</strong> and garnish with the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>parsley</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
